NEW AMAZING CAMERA = BYE BYE LUXLOVED77!!



YEEEEAH. After 2 long years and 12 days of this journal I'm finally getting a new one dedicated to the awesomeness awesome, my baby, my love, my..

Powershot Pro1 WHOOOT!:


Yeah, so everyone should go right this second and add

www.livejournal.com/users/_shakeappeal

for some of the hot new action.  Don't be offended if you're not added right away, it's going to take me a while to convert all the shit. But still... add a bitch.

BYE FEINDS.

That is what beauty looks like.

I can't describe last night because nothing I say will do it any justice.

The 8 of us lined up in the front, singing every single word, dancing to every single song, screaming at the top of our lungs... I've never felt anything like it. Bailey, Virginia, Ashley and I were seriously the ONLY people there who could literally sing every single word, new CD and old, and that felt so cool, because they totally saw and they knew that we were genuine and not some stupid art fuck hipsters like basically everyone else there.  How goddamn lame can you get. Why do you stand in the front row if you're not going to dance and you're going to judge everyone who does?

I can't describe how I felt during Calculation Theme.  Or Dead Disco.  Emily has this power and it's indescribable.  She was saying things during Dead Disco and I just wanted to start sobbing because it was things that I've been feeling so much lately and I loved knowing that this person that I basically idolize completely agrees with me and knows how I'm feeling. And it was so comfortable being surrounded by the people that I knew also agreed and felt the same way. My support system.

Last night may have been one of the best nights of my life.

In order to love Must Love Dogs, you Must Love Shit.













OHHHHHHH!!!!!

Hey look at me, I got a new layout.  It's not that different but I've been obsessing over this David Lachapelle picture for like, 3 years so I decided to make good use out of it.

I think I'm going to make my journal half friends only, half not.  So we'll see how that works out.

Mkay bye.
Mmm. Friends Only. Comment.
